    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain chassis torsional rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the precise turn-in and tactile feedback characteristic of the M-chassis. Mechanically robust and optimized for performance, this is a sorted example for the discerning driver.",
